docs.text: Usage # Reporting for cppCheck Metrics # Summarized and scored metrics Rolled up for all directories below current <directory name> Metrics contains rolled up metrics for <directory name> File Metric contains metric for individual file in <directory name> Reports # Direct Circular File References File 1 depends on File 2 Count times File 2 depends on File 1 Count times File Dependencies All files in source tree listed Depends ON files table Depends BY files table Count is the number of dependencies for the file File List Indent Indented source file listing Includes cumulative SLOC count Red Metrics Listing by metric type for files that contain at least one red metric for item(s) within the file Searches # Searches do not work when opening site/index.html file directly from web browser Searches worked when opening site/index.html file from web server In terminal window move to site directory Start web server at command prompt: python3 -m http.server Open http://127.0.0.1:8000/index.html in web browser About # Static site generated by Mkdocs from custom Python scripts and a Scitools Understand database
